1959;;The Crowning Touch;;British;;David Eady;;Ted Ray, Greta Gynt;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Crowning_Touch;;The "Crowning Touch" of the title is a fancy ladies hat. It has been ordered and specially set aside at a posh British hat shop, but no one has come to collect it. Three of the shop's staff offer different reasons as to why the pretty young girl who'd ordered the hat never showed up.